    "body": "I built CentryAI because I have ADHD and was paying for 11 subscriptions I hadn't used in months. Most trackers make you enter everything manually — that doesn't work if you've forgotten what you're paying for. CentryAI scans your Gmail or iCloud, finds every recurring charge, and scores which ones you're not using. The real pain is cancelling. CentryAI's Cancel Finder locates the exact cancellation page in one tap. No bank linking. Emails are never stored. Available in 18 languages.",
